title: Girls Aloud Discography (Albums + Singles + More) 320 kbps
description:
Girls Aloud Discography

This collection includes all of the Girls Aloud studio albums, singles (including b-sides), and a few extras.  I didn't include any repeats, so if a track is missing from a folder, it means it's in another folder (e.g. Biology is in the Chemistry Album folder, but not in the Biology Single folder).  Basically, all of the tracks are 320 kbps (below I specify which aren't).  I bought a lot of these tracks, so you probably won't be able to find some at this quality in another torrent.  If you have any questions, problems, GA request--please leave a comment.  Thanks a lot and enjoy :)
